----- stdout -----
Generate random & valid Semantic Version Strings. They may be large and awkward, but valid Semantic Versions. Useful for testing and validation

Usage: sem-tool generate [OPTIONS] [COUNT]

Arguments:
  [COUNT]  How many to create (default 1) [default: 1]

Options:
  -s, --small                "Small" will ensure the MAJOR, MINOR & PATCH components are under [u64::MAX]
      --mcp                  Run an MCP server over stdio that exposes this CLI's clap schema
      --export-skills <DIR>  Generate Agent Skills (SKILL.md) from tools, resources, and prompts, then exit
  -h, --help                 Print help

